sequenceDiagram
    participant Agent
    participant RLM as rlm-factory_query<br>(query_cache.py)
    participant VDB as vector-db_query<br>(query.py)
    participant Ledger as RLM Ledger<br>(JSON)
    participant Chroma as ChromaDB<br>(Vector Store)

    Note over Agent, Ledger: Phase 1: High-Speed Orientation (O(1))
    
    Agent->>RLM: "What does the vector query tool do?"
    RLM->>Ledger: Key/Value Lookup
    Ledger-->>RLM: "query.py handles semantic search..."
    RLM-->>Agent: Returns 1-Sentence Summary
    
    alt Summary Sufficient
        Agent->>Agent: Proceed with high-level planning
        Note right of Agent: "I know enough to continue."
    else Summary Insufficient
        Note over Agent, Chroma: Phase 2: Targeted Deep Dive (Semantic)
        Agent->>VDB: "Find exact code for vector semantic search"
        VDB->>Chroma: Nearest-neighbor embedding search
        Chroma-->>VDB: Ranked Chunks + Super-RAG Context
        VDB-->>Agent: Returns exact file snippets
        Agent->>Agent: Perform deep analysis
    end
